-----Original Message-----
From: Rebecca Small [mailto:rsmall@...]
Sent: Tuesday, July 03, 2001 9:01 AM
To: 'eqbards@yahoogroups.com'
Subject: [eqbards] Finally!


I'm finally done with my epic! I knew it would be soon as the Maestro
finally dropped a 7 string when we were in Hate last Saturday. That meant of
course I would soon finish the epic and not need the lute. I do have a
question that I have not seen a clear answer on: is the epic as powerful as
all our best instruments or stronger in string, lesser in percussion? I'm
just trying to figure out what instruments I don't need to carry around
anymore.

Brilinnia Ban'Sidhe
Venator Sapentia, Xegony
